# workload (cluster) infra


## Howto write the declarative configuration for workload infra
- base infra specifying openstack/k8s info (eg. Host OS, cluster version)
- optional "extensions/additions" (eg. multus, NSM, DANM, OVS and VPP-networking vswitch) to the base workload infra 

Document Specification for possible workload infra configurations


## Examples of declarative configuration

- K8s + DANM
- NSM + K8s
- OpenStack-VPP + K8s + NSM
- OpenStack-OVS

